Eponym is a state-of-the-art generative algorithm that produces fine, abstract art, in under 1 minute, using an innovative text-to-image generator. Any word or phrase, can be transformed into a beautiful 1/1 art piece, forever etched onto the Ethereum blockchain as the visual representation of your phrase.
